OL,6,FWages have outpaced prices for the
OL,7,Flast two years, but many households
OL,8,Fare still feeling bruised by the last
OL,9,Fwave of inflation, which broke three
OL,10,Fyears ago.
OL,12,FThe government recognises most
OL,13,Fhouseholds aren't feeling better off.
OL,15,F"I know working people are still
OL,16,Fstruggling with the cost of living,"
OL,17,Fsaid the chancellor in a statement
OL,18,Fthis morning.
