OL,6,F"That is why we have already taken
OL,7,Faction by increasing the national
OL,8,Fminimum wage for three million
OL,9,Fworkers, rolling out free breakfast
OL,10,Fclubs in every primary school and
OL,11,Fextending the #3 bus fare cap."
OL,13,FWhile inflation is unlikely to reach
OL,14,Fprevious heights, it is forecast to
OL,15,Fremain stubbornly high in the months
OL,16,Fahead.
OL,18,F"Is an August rate cut in jeopardy?
OL,19,FNo, we don't think so," says Sanjay
OL,20,FRaja, chief UK economist at Deutsche
OL,21,FBank.
